            <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
                <h3>
                    University of Utah <span class="logo-placeholder"
                        ><img
                            src="/utah.jpg"
                            alt="Utah Logo"
                            class="edu-logo"
                            style="height: 24px;"
                        /></span
                    >
                </h3>
                <p class="role">
                    I will be attending <a href="https://www.cs.utah.edu/"
                        >Kahlert School of Computing</a
                    >, <a href="https://www.utah.edu/">University of Utah</a> as a
                    visiting scholar during the summer of 2026, where I will complete
                    a student intership of several months under the guidance of Preofessor
                    <a href="https://yangzzzy.github.io/">Yin Yang</a>. I hope I
                    will have a fulfilling and enjoyable internship experience.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
